title: ***Open For Tours On Weekends - Newly Renovated - Endless Amenities***
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', '-Promenade Bike Trail and Bicycle Storage', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Certified 100% sprinklered apartments', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-Moen Align bathroom collection in a chrome finish for a modern look', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
